<section xmlns:ns0="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude">
  <num>21-588</num>
  <heading>Forms.</heading>
  <text>All applications and certificates for the hospitalization of a person in the District of Columbia under this chapter shall be made on forms approved by the Commission on Mental Health and furnished by it.</text>
